title: Introducing: Benched with Bonnetta
itunes:title: Introducing: Benched with Bonnetta
description:
In the newest podcast from the NFL, Benched with Bonnetta, Rachel Bonnetta talks you through the latest NFL headlines in the only way she knows how: very, very, very seriously. The Benched with Bonnetta Podcast launches January 25th with new episodes every Tuesday.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
